channel.title: *Updated*[Delta]Mickey Mouse's Keyblade[Kingdom Hearts]
channel.description:
Now my friend got into modeling for his and my private server and would like to show off his first model. I'm sure this will be great when it is fully finish, but as of right now its only 90% done. After about a days work he is going to try animate it so without anymore further words here it is and hope you like and remember this is his "FIRST" model.
*Model of it* [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/r2q846.jpg[/img]
*me holding it* [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/dcftky.png[/img]
*side view of me holding it* [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/1zvu1yp.png[/img]
*drop* [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/117u3k1.png[/img]
Thanks for viewing these photos and here is a link more about this keyblade if you want to know [url=http://www.khwiki.net/Kingdom_Key_D]http://www.khwiki.net/Kingdom_Key_D[/url]
